# Model artifacts are stored here.
#
# This directory is tracked in git (via this file) but model *.pkl files are
# excluded via .gitignore.
#
# To generate the model artifact, run from the project root:
#
#   python scripts/generate_dataset.py   # creates data/training_data.csv
#   python scripts/train_model.py        # trains and saves models/waf_ai_model.pkl
